storyInfo: All roads have been paved. She has uncovered her past.

attributes.content: Back up, this one's tricky.
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Don't fight her head on.
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Cover the aisles and the stairs leading up to the Donna's box!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Tsk, tsk. Rossati soldiers are pretty capable after all, huh.
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: Looks like trying to brute force my way through isn't a realistic option.
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: Hmm...
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: Haha, silly Texas. It's pretty obvious she's got a recorder in that bass.
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: Sounds convincing, though, the way she's plucking those strings.
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: Haha, there it is.
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: If I can't break through the front... I'll just have to make a path!
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: Don't panic!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Stand your ground!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Gah, aren't you afraid to die?
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: Guh... Urgh...
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: How are the others doing?
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: The aisles and stairs leading to Giovanna's box are all guarded.
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: They were ready for this.
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: Leave it to the Rossatis...
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: But, we've never been ones to underestimate Giovanna.
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: Throw more soldiers at them. We're not letting Giovanna out today.
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: You might not have underestimated Giovanna, but don't you think you underestimated me?
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: What—
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: You're... Wallach.
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: Heh, had I known the show today would've been so exciting, I wouldn't have gone to buy a drink for the Donna.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: If Signora Giovanna appreciates a fine wine, I happen to have a selection with me.
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: No thanks.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: The Donna enjoys many things about Siracusa, but the wine isn't one.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Siracusan wines are too weak, same as you people swing your weapons. Doesn't make for a good time.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Maybe you just haven't tried the best Siracusa has to offer.
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: So, isn't this a great opportunity?
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Do you know how long I've been waiting for this?
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Bellones and Saluzzos, let's find out what Siracusa's finest wine really tastes like.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Trying to get up this way?
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Stop her!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Who said I was going up?
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: What? Explosives?!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Get outta there!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Woah, the seats over yonder just collapsed!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Is that... Lappland?!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Look over there!
attributes.name: Horrified Audience

attributes.content: Urgh...
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: I-Is it another famiglie gang war...?
attributes.name: Horrified Audience

attributes.content: Move.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Sh-She had weapons in her instrument?!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Texas!
attributes.name: Sora

attributes.content: Texas says nothing. She only shoots her a glance, parting her lips for a second before rushing up the stairs.
Sora reads those lips.
She said: 'Wait for me.'
Aaaaaahhh—! Run! Run for it!
attributes.name: Panicked Audience

attributes.content: What'cha think we oughta do, Exusiai? Sora's in danger!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: But—
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: S-Someone, save me—
attributes.name: Horrified Audience

attributes.content: Get down!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Woah, you're pretty tough for an old guy.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Do I look that old to you?
Uhh... Well, I guess I wouldn't go that far.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Looks like today's performance is not 'La Morte di Texas,' but rather 'La Morte di Rossati.'
Find somewhere to hide, children.
That sounds nice, but our friend is still up there on stage.
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: It's a gat-danged hurricane all 'round the thing! We can't just go hoppin' on into that!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Let's go backstage then!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Okay!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: C'mon, outta my way!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Go, brave children.
Thanks, old man!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: I'll buy you a slice later!
attributes.name: Exusiai

attributes.content: Thank ya kindly!
attributes.name: Croissant

attributes.content: Haha, kids these days are so full of pep.
What's your plan now, Giovanna?
Donna Giovanna, we've got everything locked down. Let's get you out, while we still can.
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Why?
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: It's a rare opportunity to watch a wonderful show from a fantastic seat. I'm going to have to savor this.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: Sora, you really are her true friend, aren't you?
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: Now, how are you going to get up here, Cellinia?
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: Even if you find a shortcut, getting to me won't be easy.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: But—
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: If I were to run away right now, do you think the Bellones and Saluzzos would just give up and call it quits?
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: This is a war now, my dear.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: The Bellones and Saluzzos have decided to Signora Sicilia's ban on violence, and started a gang war.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: Spread the word. There's only one thing we can do now: fight to the end.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: Of course.
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Nngh...
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: Looks like 'fine Siracusan wine' was nothing special after all.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: I wouldn't gloat just yet... Columbian scum...
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: What—
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: Yes, I know. You Siracusans think the Columbian famiglie are just rowdy upstarts who haven't paid our dues.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: And yeah, there are a whole lot of incompetent idiots over in Columbia.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: But what about you?
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Can you even sniff out the scent of blood under your so-called 'guns and order?'
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: We've never looked down on Siracusa.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: But from what I've seen today, you don't even deserve my attention.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Wallach, we've got a situation at the theater!
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Someone blew the seats, and Cellinia is heading straight for the third floor.
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: You've got five seconds for your last words.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Last words?
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: Heh, what's there to say?
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: If you're really gonna do it, then tell Leontuzzo that I'm sorry.
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: Sure.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: What—
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Leon?!
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: You...
attributes.name: Demetri

attributes.content: I'll handle this my way, Demetri.
attributes.name: Leontuzzo

attributes.content: Signor Leontuzzo. Here I thought we could get along.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: You just lost your last chance for that.
attributes.name: Leontuzzo

attributes.content: Well, well, well. Turns out the heir to a great famiglia just oozes charisma after all.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: You've made a fool of me, and still you tell me I had a chance to make things right.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: What's done is done.
attributes.name: Leontuzzo

attributes.content: I'll make you a bet, Wallach.
attributes.name: Leontuzzo

attributes.content: You're a betting man?
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Hahahaha! Signor Leon, mio amico, we're not in a dining hall or one of our offices.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: We're in a war, and only one of us walking out of this alive.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Trust me, you'll love this one.
attributes.name: Leontuzzo

attributes.content: Ugh, these Rossatis are a pain in the ass.
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: Your Honor? We never heard you were joining us on this one.
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: And anyway, this ain't something you can just walk into.
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: I'm not here to stop you. I'm not interested.
attributes.name: Lavinia

attributes.content: I'm looking for someone.
attributes.name: Lavinia

attributes.content: Who?
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: We got one helluva mess here. Not gonna be easy to find anybody.
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: All I need from you is to stay out of my way.
attributes.name: Lavinia

attributes.content: But...
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: Even if I die here, that's none of Famiglia Bellone's business.
attributes.name: Lavinia

attributes.content: Suit yourself then.
attributes.name: Bellone Mafioso

attributes.content: There you are.
attributes.name: Lavinia

attributes.content: Hold it.
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: I work here.
attributes.name: Carwash Worker

attributes.content: Uh huh. We got rid of all the workers.
attributes.name: Rossati Mafioso

attributes.content: Grr, what is he doing here?
attributes.name: Lavinia

attributes.content: Look out, Dan—
attributes.name: Lavinia

attributes.content: Blood splatters, and a few drops splash across Lavinia's face.
Signorina Lavinia.
attributes.name: Carwash Worker

attributes.content: What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Carwash Worker

attributes.content: The 'path' opened by Lappland is doing its job. Only a short distance separates her from her old friend.
She lets out a soft sigh.
Chaos swirls all around her, but she knows what to do.
I knew you'd come, Cellinia.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: What a look in your eyes there. It's like I'm the prey.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Let's see what the Last Texas can do!
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Signor, Director... is this chaos... part of the show?
attributes.name: Rubio

attributes.content: Chaos?
attributes.name: Bernardo

attributes.content: In my opinion, Segretario Rubio, everything is in perfect order.
attributes.name: Bernardo

attributes.content: What comes next will be even better.
attributes.name: Bernardo

attributes.content: ...I see.
attributes.name: Rubio

attributes.content: You lead one of the most prestigious troupes in Volsinii, and you've put on a play unlike any other.
attributes.name: Rubio

attributes.content: We do have an intermission coming up, though. You may tell me what it is you want from me.
attributes.name: Bernardo

attributes.content: What I want... isn't very complicated.
attributes.name: Rubio

attributes.content: With Carracci's death, the seat of Ministro dei Lavori Pubblici is now vacant.
attributes.name: Rubio

attributes.content: You must be thinking about who the most suitable candidate is.
attributes.name: Rubio

attributes.content: I take it you've decided you're that candidate?
attributes.name: Bernardo

attributes.content: I don't think there's anyone else better suited than me.
attributes.name: Rubio

attributes.content: *cough* *cough*, *cough*, *cough*...
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Wow... There's still mercy in you, at a time like this...
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: The Saluzzo Psycho isn't gonna finish me off?
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: I'm not interested in a pointless fight with some punk who was never taking it seriously to begin with.
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: ...Hah.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: What are you waiting for? What do you want?
attributes.name: Lappland

attributes.content: I made a bet with someone. And I hope I lose.
attributes.name: Wallach

attributes.content: Wallach looks in the direction Texas went. No one can stop her from assassinating Giovanna.
Except Giovanna herself.
There is nobody else in the empty room.
Texas immediately realizes what's happening, but it's too late. A knife is already up against her neck.
Since I came to Siracusa, I've been thinking of all the different ways someone might try to kill me.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: But I never once thought it might be you.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: And I never imagined you'd let your guard down, at a time like this.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: Did you think that when I saw you'd, I'd give you a big hug and cry 'thank goodness, Cellinia, you're still alive?'
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: And then we'd sit down and share a drink and catch up on everything that's happened over the last few years?
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: I'm here to kill you.
attributes.name: Texas

attributes.content: Great.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: With that word, Giovanna drops the knife in her hand.
She wears a radiant smile on her face, her expression full of longing, as if the murderous intent from a moment ago was but a light-hearted joke.
Long time no see, Cellinia.
attributes.name: Giovanna

attributes.content: Long time no see, Giovanna.
attributes.name: Texas
